This script will retrieve some keys information about the system
First thing, we want to make sure that only root account can run the script, we'll retieve information like:

 Information about the OS and kernel version 

 Last successful connection

 Last unsuccessful connection

 Display information about users

 Modify the validity information of a password

 List the allowed commands for users

 User information

 Path Environment

 Connected devices

 Partitions

 Block Devices

 Check for ufw status

 Open PortS with net-tools utility

 ModifiCation on APT directory

 Chrootkit and Rkhunter for finding most common and famous rootkit

 Intrusion Detection System - Snort

 Monitoring interface

 Clamav antivirus

 displays all processes

 Firewall Logs



